  (text "EXPANSION NOTES:\\nAll Qwiic and Grove signals from STM32U585 (UNO Q MCU)\\nESP32-S3 and ESP32-C6 do NOT drive these connectors\\nQwiic: J_Q1/J_Q2 daisy-chain (electrically parallel)\\n  4.7kΩ pullups R_X1/R_X2 on SDA/SCL to +3V3\\nGrove: J_GI2C J_GURT J_GSPI J_GDIG J_GANL\\n  All 3.3V max. Do not connect 5V Grove sensors.\\nJ_PSSI: 12-pin 2.54mm PSSI parallel interface breakout\\nJ_I2C4: 4-pin 2.54mm I2C4 breakout (camera CCI bus)\\nJ_OPA: 4-pin 2.54mm OpAmp input/output breakout"
